query:
SELECT name, plannedVisitDate, FROM_UNIXTIME(plannedVisitDate/1000) as date_readable 
FROM tourist_sites 
WHERE tripId = 30001 AND (plannedVisitDate = 1788307200000 OR plannedVisitDate = 1788652800000)
ORDER BY plannedVisitDate, plannedVisitTime;
